author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Three prop replicas, an incredible treasure trove of vintage woodworking magazines, and a paper conservation supplies make up this year-end round up of mailbag show and tells. Thanks to Vince, Jonathan, Roy, and the team at Talas for these lovely gift packages!

Voyagers! Omni Prop Replica: https://www.etsy.com/listing/1212752348/voyagers-omni-prop-replica-brass-dial
Light up Krypton Knowledge Crystal replica: https://www.etsy.com/listing/1871200602/light-up-krypton-knowledge-crystal
Wood Gem cabinets: https://www.woodgemcustomcabinets.com/
Talas Conservation, Archival, and Bookbinding supplies: https://www.talasonline.com/
Adam at the NPS Museum Conservation Lab: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3J-ToojchA&list=PLJtitKU0CAej3AzM9RgtGQ2146AL4VAOK

Shot and edited by Joey Fameli
Music by Jinglepunks
